{"tid":837338,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疑假冒「東網」行騙 透露香港人 1 蚊買到三星 Galaxy S9 方法","createTime":"2018-09-26T09:56:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T12:39:33.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"639dc3a85d069eae8ce72ce4998d8c70a37c74f9","tid":837338,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:56:18.000Z","msg":"近日網上出現了一個內含套取個人資料陷阱的假網頁，文章第一段寫著「如果你居住在香港，想買一部全新三星 Galaxy S9，接下來的文章就會讓你興奮」，內容講述如何利用港幣 1 元就可購得 Samsung Galaxy S9 。這個版面設計與香港傳媒東網（<a href=\"http://On.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FOn.cc&d=1x%2BWbh8gi2e5EyRCu49XCLDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=806e30c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">On.cc</a>）極為相似的網頁，左上更有東網 Logo ，但其實是一個疑似名為「Myphone.fun」的網站假冒製作，內含輸入用戶個人資料的欄位，因此網民應極為注意，避免受騙。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2018-09-25-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%884.38.30-694x426.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2018-09-25-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25884.38.30-694x426.png&h=c32e652c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這個網頁的網址為「<a href=\"http://myphone.fun/2018/09/01/研究称三星智能手机出货量今年将跌破3亿-为2013年来/?eid=hs4」，在\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmyphone.fun%2F2018%2F09%2F01%2F%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E5%87%BA%E8%B4%A7%E9%87%8F%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E5%B0%86%E8%B7%8C%E7%A0%B43%E4%BA%BF-%E4%B8%BA2013%E5%B9%B4%E6%9D%A5%2F%3Feid%3Dhs4%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8&d=1x%2BWbh8gi2e5EyRCu49XCLDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=1a6a28ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://myphone.fun/2018/09/01/研究称三星智能手机出货量今年将跌破3亿-为2013年来/?eid=hs4」，在</a> Myphone.fun 網站中點擊第一段新聞亦能同樣打開這篇假網頁。假網頁模仿香港傳媒「東網 <a href=\"http://On.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FOn.cc&d=1x%2BWbh8gi2e5EyRCu49XCLDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=806e30c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">On.cc</a>」的頁面設計模式，兼用上東網官方標誌，如不看網址列又不加提防，有機會相信該網頁的假新聞描述。<br />\n<br />\n該假冒網頁提到三星在香港市場的份額下跌，因此推出全新行銷計劃，希望用戶在港幣 1 元購入 Samsung Galaxy S9 之後可在朋友之間分享。假冒網頁提供「1蚊一部Galaxy S9」的登記連結，連結會跳到一個網站，要求用戶輸入個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n為免受騙，網民打開類似網站頁面時需要非常小心，並留意網址列所示的網址是否為假冒網站。"},{"pid":"265a5569e3b3cb89bb0b43f18840b97fc40ca9de","tid":837338,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T10:02:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/09/25/fake1hkdollarsamsunggalaxys9/tech-secure/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2Ffake1hkdollarsamsunggalaxys9%2Ftech-secure%2F&d=1x%2BWbh8gi2e5EyRCu49XCLDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=6ecbe68c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/09/25/fake1hkdollarsamsunggalaxys9/tech-secure/</a>"},{"pid":"50090826d57bfb4c08e99ceeb637c48694508794","tid":837338,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T11:26:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e5277a3865e4c4294cd6937e304f95caaea8548","tid":837338,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T11:32:10.000Z","msg":"諗起哩條柒碌，post都del埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會員加辣(uid:206041)假冒東方報業名義發放虛假消息<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/bBecMS\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/bBecMS</a>"},{"pid":"a495505cc9f97b65d7fc0c27bb831c6a224f3f91","tid":837338,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50090826d57bfb4c08e99ceeb637c48694508794","tid":837338,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T11:26:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T11:47:39.000Z","msg":"得罪東方&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/asse